      <title>新加坡终止追捕洗钱嫌疑人，他们损失了 14 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/singapore-ends-pursuit-of-money-launderers-at-large-who-forfeited-1-4-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡警方结束了对涉嫌该国有史以来最大洗钱丑闻的 15 名嫌疑人的追捕，此前这些嫌疑人同意向当局交出总额为 18.5 亿新元（14 亿美元）的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/singapore-ends-pursuit-of-money-launderers-at-large-who-forfeited-1-4-billion</guid>
